        {
            "title": "亞洲匯市與美元波動有限,交易員關注伊朗戰事最新進展;印度央行措施提振盧比",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bYeyRruf.sU9TLI5qD0KbA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEF140ZJ_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週五亞洲貨幣在窄幅區間內交易,投資者因中東衝突升級的討論而保持警惕,而由於耶穌受難日假期導致流動性不足,市場波動受到抑制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元在前一交易日上漲0.4%後保持穩定,受惠於美國總統川普就伊朗問題發表評論後風險規避情緒升溫。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>伊朗衝突持續升溫;川普誓言進一步打擊</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,華盛頓可能在未來幾週加強軍事行動,並在週四晚間的另一則貼文中警告,美軍可能瞄準橋樑和發電廠等關鍵基礎設施。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5705b1c4-48b9-3bba-acaa-1a093aa425f4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四投資者情緒曾出現一些穩定跡象,此前伊朗表示正與阿曼就管理霍爾木茲海峽航運交通的框架進行合作,緩解了對這條重要石油運輸路線供應中斷的部分擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週五日圓兌美元USD/JPY匯率持平於159.63日圓,接近備受關注的160日圓兌1美元關口,交投於159.6附近。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本財務大臣也警告稱,隨著波動性加劇,當局已準備好對外匯市場的投機性波動採取行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓元兌美元USD/KRW匯率和新加坡元兌美元USD/SGD匯率基本保持平穩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳元兌美元AUD/USD匯率基本持平。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>印度盧比進一步遠離近期創下的歷史低點</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週五印度盧比兌美元USD/INR匯率下跌0.3%至92.71盧比,此前本週初曾觸及95.22盧比的歷史高點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週該貨幣兌美元料將升值逾2%,此前印度儲備銀行的支持措施幫助穩定了該貨幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度央行限制了銀行的淨外匯敞口,並禁止它們向客戶提供無本金交割遠期合約,迫使大量投機頭寸平倉,並引發在岸市場的美元拋售。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外,人民幣在岸匯率USD/CNY下跌0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當日稍早公佈的數據顯示,中國服務業板塊增長在3月份放緩,Ratingdog服務業PMI從2月份33個月高點56.7降至52.1。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者現在將注意力轉向當日稍晚公佈的美國非農就業數據,這可能為聯準會利率前景提供進一步線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%8C%AF%E5%B8%82%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%B3%A2%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E4%BA%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E7%9B%A7%E6%AF%94-064022476.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-03 15:14:12",
